01:12:43.359 --> 01:12:44.961
The crosshairs were on us,

01:12:45.061 --> 01:12:48.164
and on me a lot.

01:12:48.264 --> 01:12:49.833
We knew our phone was tapped,

01:12:49.933 --> 01:12:52.502
we knew that we were under
surveillance a lot of time.

01:12:52.602 --> 01:12:54.638
- It took 'em another year

01:12:54.738 --> 01:12:57.173
of watching and
tapping and foll--

01:12:57.273 --> 01:12:59.008
they followed me
to Saint Martin,

01:12:59.108 --> 01:13:01.044
followed me ski trips,

01:13:01.144 --> 01:13:03.980
followed me to Europe,
followed me everywhere.

01:13:04.080 --> 01:13:05.381
They didn't catch me.

01:13:05.482 --> 01:13:06.950
They didn't catch me smuggling.

01:13:07.050 --> 01:13:08.351
They caught me with
a whole lot of money,

01:13:08.452 --> 01:13:10.019
but they didn't catch
me with any dope.

01:13:10.119 --> 01:13:13.457
- They never got any hash.

01:13:13.557 --> 01:13:16.159
So, how can you be
convicted of smuggling

01:13:16.259 --> 01:13:17.994
3000 pounds of hash,

01:13:18.094 --> 01:13:20.830
when they don't
even have one pound?

01:13:20.930 --> 01:13:22.165
They don't have an ounce.

01:13:22.265 --> 01:13:23.567
They don't have anything.

01:13:23.667 --> 01:13:25.969
- There was never a case
that the government had made

01:13:26.069 --> 01:13:30.474
that really had any substantial
criminality underlying it.

01:13:30.574 --> 01:13:32.308
They just didn't have it.

01:13:32.408 --> 01:13:34.243
So, what the
government had to do

01:13:34.343 --> 01:13:36.646
was bring the Hell's
Angels into the case,

01:13:36.746 --> 01:13:37.981
and say to the world,

01:13:38.081 --> 01:13:39.583
"These guys are working
with the Hell's Angels.

01:13:39.683 --> 01:13:40.850
"They're making acid.

01:13:40.950 --> 01:13:42.151
"Hell's Angels are
distributing the acid.

01:13:42.251 --> 01:13:43.386
"Killing everybody.

01:13:43.487 --> 01:13:45.154
"They're the nastiest
people on Earth,

01:13:45.254 --> 01:13:47.724
"so these guys can't be
any god damn good either."

01:13:47.824 --> 01:13:50.159
That was their whole
theory of the conspiracy.

01:13:50.259 --> 01:13:51.427
Put the bad together
with the good

01:13:51.528 --> 01:13:57.801
and bring the good down.

01:13:57.901 --> 01:14:00.604
- The Brotherhood indictment
was a conspiracy charge

01:14:00.704 --> 01:14:02.405
for everything, you name it.

01:14:02.506 --> 01:14:06.275
It was conspiracy engulfed
it all, from hash smuggling,

01:14:06.375 --> 01:14:07.877
weed smuggling,

01:14:07.977 --> 01:14:10.680
manufacturing of LSD.

01:14:10.780 --> 01:14:16.853
They were charged with it all.

01:14:16.953 --> 01:14:20.056
Michael and Eleanora,
our lawyers called me,

01:14:20.156 --> 01:14:23.092
and said, "I do believe

01:14:23.192 --> 01:14:26.996
"it's time to leave."

01:14:27.096 --> 01:14:28.097
- [Voiceover] Over the weekend,

01:14:28.197 --> 01:14:29.933
in a concerted multi-state raid,

01:14:30.033 --> 01:14:31.367
federal authorities
captured members

01:14:31.467 --> 01:14:33.369
of the international
drug-smuggling ring

01:14:33.469 --> 01:14:35.438
The Brotherhood of Eternal Love.

01:14:35.539 --> 01:14:37.206
- When the indictment came out,

01:14:37.306 --> 01:14:38.942
it was like (mimics explosion).

01:14:39.042 --> 01:14:41.244
They hit everywhere, they
got everybody at once.

01:14:41.344 --> 01:14:42.378
It was like, bam!

01:14:42.478 --> 01:14:43.813
You know, everybody was busted.

01:14:43.913 --> 01:14:45.782
- [Travis] They were
busting my ranch.

01:14:45.882 --> 01:14:47.884
They were busting
Chuck Scott's house.

01:14:47.984 --> 01:14:49.786
They were busting Jack
Harrington's house,

01:14:49.886 --> 01:14:51.087
looking for Gordon.

01:14:51.187 --> 01:14:53.623
They were going
after everybody, man.

01:14:53.723 --> 01:14:56.125
- [Voiceover] Federal, state,
and local narcotics officers

01:14:56.225 --> 01:14:58.461
arrested 15 of 29
persons indicted

01:14:58.562 --> 01:15:00.263
by the Orange County grand jury.

01:15:00.363 --> 01:15:01.164
- [Voiceover] Authorities seized

01:15:01.264 --> 01:15:03.099
7.9 million dollars in drugs,

01:15:03.199 --> 01:15:05.134
and two LSD laboratories.

01:15:05.234 --> 01:15:07.804
- At the time, it
was a unprecedented

01:15:07.904 --> 01:15:10.907
coordinated effort
among the feds,

01:15:11.007 --> 01:15:12.776
and all the local people;

01:15:12.876 --> 01:15:15.344
California, Oregon, Hawaii.

01:15:15.444 --> 01:15:18.414
The news people
were all over it.

01:15:18.514 --> 01:15:23.252
They were gonna put us
down once and for all.

01:15:23.352 --> 01:15:26.255
Mark Stanton, and Russell
and his wife and kids,

01:15:26.355 --> 01:15:27.523
everybody had kids,

01:15:27.624 --> 01:15:29.593
me and Carol and all,
didn't know what to do,

01:15:29.693 --> 01:15:34.197
so we went to the Barnum
and Bailey Circus.

01:15:34.297 --> 01:15:38.101
And we just sort of
stayed there all day.

01:15:38.201 --> 01:15:42.171
We could be anonymous in it.

01:15:42.271 --> 01:15:43.873
And we saw the first show,

01:15:43.973 --> 01:15:45.208
and then it got finished.

01:15:45.308 --> 01:15:47.110
Saw the next show,

01:15:47.210 --> 01:15:50.213
and we would sometimes
go out to the car

01:15:50.313 --> 01:15:51.881
and listen to the
radio a little bit,

01:15:51.981 --> 01:15:53.717
and see if we could
hear anything else.

01:15:53.817 --> 01:15:55.151
- [Voiceover] Three more member

01:15:55.251 --> 01:15:56.285
of the Brotherhood
of Eternal Love

01:15:56.385 --> 01:15:57.621
have been caught in
an overnight raid

01:15:57.721 --> 01:15:59.789
by authorities in Orange
County, California.

01:15:59.889 --> 01:16:01.157
- [Voiceover] 14 members
of The Brotherhood,

01:16:01.257 --> 01:16:04.160
including Dr. Timothy
Leary, remain fugitives.

01:16:04.260 --> 01:16:04.961
Authorities now--

01:16:05.061 --> 01:16:05.862
- That was it.

01:16:05.962 --> 01:16:08.231
That was the day that was over.

01:16:08.331 --> 01:16:10.900
You know, everything that
we had known before that

01:16:11.000 --> 01:16:12.401
was pretty much finished.

01:16:12.501 --> 01:16:14.638
- We just ran.

01:16:14.738 --> 01:16:16.840
We all just ran,

01:16:16.940 --> 01:16:23.613
and hid, with our kids.

01:16:23.713 --> 01:16:25.081
- [Carol] We were all separating

01:16:25.181 --> 01:16:27.817
and going different
places to hide out.

01:16:27.917 --> 01:16:29.052
- [Voiceover] The pre-dawn sweep

01:16:29.152 --> 01:16:30.253
of southern and
northern California,

01:16:30.353 --> 01:16:31.387
Hawaii, and Oregon,

01:16:31.487 --> 01:16:33.589
netted 1.5 million LSD tablets,

01:16:33.690 --> 01:16:35.391
30 gallons of hashish oil.

01:16:35.491 --> 01:16:37.694
- Somebody warned me that
they knew where I was

01:16:37.794 --> 01:16:39.228
and they were coming to get me.

01:16:39.328 --> 01:16:40.897
- So, Travis and I left.

01:16:40.997 --> 01:16:42.598
We left that afternoon.

01:16:42.699 --> 01:16:45.201
And we flew from
there to Belize,

01:16:45.301 --> 01:16:47.771
and then from Belize
we took a bus,

01:16:47.871 --> 01:16:50.439
and then we switched our IDs
as we crossed the border.

01:16:50.539 --> 01:16:55.244
We went into
Yucatan with new ID.

01:16:55.344 --> 01:16:57.747
- Michael and I went
to the Caribbean.

01:16:57.847 --> 01:17:00.216
We just bought
tickets, paid cash.

01:17:00.316 --> 01:17:03.286
Gone, no record, nobody.

01:17:03.386 --> 01:17:05.855
We went to the Bahamas
and Cayman Islands,

01:17:05.955 --> 01:17:08.257
and we ended up in Jamaica.

01:17:08.357 --> 01:17:11.961
We were underground for sure.

01:17:12.061 --> 01:17:13.629
We had to change our identity,

01:17:13.730 --> 01:17:14.964
but we were good at that.

01:17:15.064 --> 01:17:16.232
We were like chameleons,

01:17:16.332 --> 01:17:19.635
whatever the situation
called for, you know.

01:17:19.736 --> 01:17:21.404
Be straight, be not straight.

01:17:21.504 --> 01:17:22.972
You know, be groovy,

01:17:23.072 --> 01:17:24.941
whatever we needed to be.

01:17:25.041 --> 01:17:27.376
Our children, you know, they
all kept their first names.

01:17:27.476 --> 01:17:30.246
You know, they knew if
somebody asked them questions,

01:17:30.346 --> 01:17:32.248
they just don't answer
certain questions.

01:17:32.348 --> 01:17:36.152
They don't know,
they're just kids.

01:17:36.252 --> 01:17:39.388
I had to change their
original transcripts

01:17:39.488 --> 01:17:42.358
into a different name,

01:17:42.458 --> 01:17:47.630
so we had records to
get 'em into school.

01:17:47.731 --> 01:17:49.398
The future was uncertain.

01:17:49.498 --> 01:17:52.736
- [Michael R.] I did not know
when we went to New Mexico

01:17:52.836 --> 01:17:55.238
what was gonna happen.

01:17:55.338 --> 01:17:58.574
I bought some jewelry equipment
and stone cutting equipment,

01:17:58.674 --> 01:18:02.345
and I started making
a living with that.

01:18:02.445 --> 01:18:05.581
- We were just at the crest
of the wave of the big boom

01:18:05.681 --> 01:18:07.616
of Indian turquoise jewelry,

01:18:07.717 --> 01:18:11.420
when it went off in the 70s.

01:18:11.520 --> 01:18:13.622
- Well, I spent 11
years as a fugitive.

01:18:13.723 --> 01:18:15.424
Raised my family as a fugitive,

01:18:15.524 --> 01:18:17.193
living all over world.

01:18:17.293 --> 01:18:20.263
And I actually hooked
up with Michael Randall,

01:18:20.363 --> 01:18:23.867
and Chuck Scott who I
hadn't seen in years.

01:18:23.967 --> 01:18:25.534
Kind of rejoined the crew.

01:18:25.634 --> 01:18:27.370
I bought a ton of hash,

01:18:27.470 --> 01:18:30.439
so I gave them the whole
Moroccan load to sell.

01:18:30.539 --> 01:18:35.178
I just let them do it,
and they moved it all.

01:18:35.278 --> 01:18:37.180
- We were in the studio one day,

01:18:37.280 --> 01:18:39.648
and the phone rang and
it was from Travis,

01:18:39.749 --> 01:18:41.617
and I could hear
the conversation,

01:18:41.717 --> 01:18:43.219
Michael talking to 'em,

01:18:43.319 --> 01:18:49.358
Something inside me just
knew something was wrong.

01:18:49.458 --> 01:18:54.563
- They tapped every phone
in the town of Long Pine.

01:18:54.663 --> 01:18:56.232
Me and a guy named Bill

01:18:56.332 --> 01:18:58.968
were taking a Cayman Airways
flight over the Grand Canyon.

01:18:59.068 --> 01:19:02.505
We got on the plane,
and the door closes.

01:19:02.605 --> 01:19:04.140
The plane pulls
away from the gate.

01:19:04.240 --> 01:19:05.374
It was about three feet.

01:19:05.474 --> 01:19:07.343
It pulls back up.

01:19:07.443 --> 01:19:09.678
The door opens, these
guys come on board,

01:19:09.779 --> 01:19:11.347
two or three of 'em, memory ...

01:19:11.447 --> 01:19:13.482
They come up, stop
right at my row,

01:19:13.582 --> 01:19:15.651
look at me and go,
"Mr. Ashbrook?"

01:19:15.751 --> 01:19:18.154
I hadn't used the name in years,

01:19:18.254 --> 01:19:19.522
years, and years.

01:19:19.622 --> 01:19:20.890
I just didn't even look up.

01:19:20.990 --> 01:19:23.426
"Mr. Ashbrook?

01:19:23.526 --> 01:19:24.994
"Come with us, please."

01:19:31.034 --> 01:19:33.436
- [Voiceover] I had met this
guy through Chuck Scott,

01:19:33.536 --> 01:19:35.038
from the east coast

01:19:35.138 --> 01:19:38.541
who had been bringing in
Pakistani hash on airplanes.

01:19:38.641 --> 01:19:41.444
And he had somebody at
the airport in New York

01:19:41.544 --> 01:19:43.346
that would clear it.

01:19:43.446 --> 01:19:44.580
I met Kitting,

01:19:44.680 --> 01:19:46.249
he seemed like a straight
shooter, good guy.

01:19:46.349 --> 01:19:49.085
So I fly to Afghanistan,
and I land I Kabul.

01:19:49.185 --> 01:19:51.554
And when I'm walking
up to immigration,

01:19:51.654 --> 01:19:53.289
they see my name on my passport,

01:19:53.389 --> 01:19:54.891
and I'm red-listed.

01:19:54.991 --> 01:19:57.093
So, all of a sudden,
everything's different

01:19:57.193 --> 01:20:00.063
than anything I'd experienced
flying in there before.

01:20:00.163 --> 01:20:06.335
A guy says, "I need
you to come with me."

01:20:06.435 --> 01:20:09.973
- I was on the run
for about 10 years.

01:20:10.073 --> 01:20:11.574
After I got back to America,

01:20:11.674 --> 01:20:13.709
when I was back in
California permanently,

01:20:13.809 --> 01:20:17.446
I didn't have any ID
for about eight years.

01:20:17.546 --> 01:20:19.782
One day I'm moving Wendy
up to northern California,

01:20:19.883 --> 01:20:21.617
and I've got big pickup truck,

01:20:21.717 --> 01:20:23.419
and it's filled with her stuff,

01:20:23.519 --> 01:20:25.889
where I can't see behind me.

01:20:25.989 --> 01:20:28.157
And I pull into
this liquor store,

01:20:28.257 --> 01:20:29.993
but I kinda miss
the entrance to it,

01:20:30.093 --> 01:20:31.260
and I had to back up,

01:20:31.360 --> 01:20:32.495
but I couldn't tell if
anyone was behind me,

01:20:32.595 --> 01:20:33.429
and I couldn't see him.

01:20:33.529 --> 01:20:34.497
So, I backed the truck up,

01:20:34.597 --> 01:20:35.764
and I pulled around,

01:20:35.865 --> 01:20:37.833
pulled into the little
convenience store,

01:20:37.934 --> 01:20:39.435
whatever market was there,

01:20:39.535 --> 01:20:41.737
and I jumped out of my
truck and I looked back,

01:20:41.837 --> 01:20:43.139
and my car's like this,

01:20:43.239 --> 01:20:45.641
and a cop car's
parked right there,

01:20:45.741 --> 01:20:46.943
and he's got his window down,

01:20:47.043 --> 01:20:48.677
and he's goin' like this.

01:20:48.777 --> 01:20:51.280
And he tells me, "Well, you
almost hit me back there.

01:20:51.380 --> 01:20:52.348
"You know that?"

01:20:52.448 --> 01:20:53.516
I said, "I know,
I couldn't see,

01:20:53.616 --> 01:20:54.918
"but I didn't hit you, right?"

01:20:55.018 --> 01:20:58.087
He said, "No, but you
really came close though.

01:20:58.187 --> 01:21:01.590
He says, "Well, let
me see your license."

01:21:01.690 --> 01:21:02.791
And I told him ...

01:21:02.892 --> 01:21:04.360
I kind of hemmed and hawed,

01:21:04.460 --> 01:21:06.462
and he said, "You don't
have a license, do you?"

01:21:06.562 --> 01:21:10.866
I told him, "No."

01:21:10.967 --> 01:21:12.135
- [Michael R.] Chuck
Scott was killed

01:21:12.235 --> 01:21:16.405
by US Marshals in Mill Valley.

01:21:16.505 --> 01:21:19.475
- Shot him in the head
as he was running,

01:21:19.575 --> 01:21:22.946
in front of his
wife and his baby,

01:21:23.046 --> 01:21:25.949
and she was pregnant.

01:21:26.049 --> 01:21:27.984
Police were going to
my parents' house,

01:21:28.084 --> 01:21:32.888
telling 'em, "You know, we
just shot Chuck in the back.

01:21:32.989 --> 01:21:35.124
"You better tell us where
your son and daughter are.

01:21:35.224 --> 01:21:36.859
"You know, because
when we find 'em,

01:21:36.960 --> 01:21:38.627
"we're not going
to ask questions.

01:21:38.727 --> 01:21:43.232
"We're going to be shooting."

01:21:43.332 --> 01:21:46.135
- We were living
outside of Boulder.

01:21:46.235 --> 01:21:48.404
It was a little
town called Lions,

01:21:48.504 --> 01:21:52.308
out where it's really
in the country.

01:21:52.408 --> 01:21:53.742
It was a hot summer day,

01:21:53.842 --> 01:21:56.512
and I had, I was studying for my

01:21:56.612 --> 01:22:00.383
GIA Diamond Certificate class.

01:22:00.483 --> 01:22:01.717
I'm studying for it,

01:22:01.817 --> 01:22:04.020
and my son, Daniel,
is takin' a nap.

01:22:04.120 --> 01:22:05.989
He's sleepin' in my lap,

01:22:06.089 --> 01:22:08.257
and the front door was open.

01:22:08.357 --> 01:22:10.559
I didn't even hear
their cars come.

01:22:10.659 --> 01:22:16.932
(ominous music)

01:22:17.033 --> 01:22:19.668
- We were down in the
lower part of our house.

01:22:19.768 --> 01:22:22.171
It was like a sunken room.

01:22:22.271 --> 01:22:26.442
I stood up, and I looked out,

01:22:26.542 --> 01:22:29.945
and I could see all these men

01:22:30.046 --> 01:22:35.151
surrounding our
house with rifles.

01:22:35.251 --> 01:22:36.919
And I went over, and I said,

01:22:37.020 --> 01:22:39.222
"Honey, they're here."

01:22:39.322 --> 01:22:40.723
And he said, "Who?

01:22:40.823 --> 01:22:43.092
"The kids are back from
the beach already?"

01:22:43.192 --> 01:22:47.430
I said, "No, they're here."

01:22:47.530 --> 01:22:49.532
I made Michael promise me

01:22:49.632 --> 01:22:52.768
that he would not panic and run.

01:22:56.805 --> 01:23:00.043
- [Michael R.] They came
charging in pointing 45s at me,

01:23:00.143 --> 01:23:00.976
and I'm trying to tell them,

01:23:01.077 --> 01:23:03.712
"I have a child in my lap."

01:23:03.812 --> 01:23:10.019
You know, be careful.

01:23:10.119 --> 01:23:13.256
- They allowed us
to hug and kiss.

01:23:13.356 --> 01:23:15.658
They handcuffed him,

01:23:15.758 --> 01:23:17.326
and that's when they drove away.

01:23:28.371 --> 01:23:31.374
(somber music)

01:23:52.561 --> 01:23:54.597
The 60s had its casualties.

01:23:54.697 --> 01:23:57.466
It wasn't just a clean
ride for everybody.

01:23:57.566 --> 01:24:01.604
And I know that
more than anybody.

01:24:01.704 --> 01:24:05.941
But, through all trials,
tribulation, and suffering,

01:24:06.041 --> 01:24:08.811
we never ever lost faith.

01:24:08.911 --> 01:24:11.614
There was so much at stake.

01:24:11.714 --> 01:24:13.149
We were a unit,

01:24:13.249 --> 01:24:14.783
and whatever we went through,

01:24:14.883 --> 01:24:16.652
we went through together,

01:24:16.752 --> 01:24:18.154
as a group,

01:24:18.254 --> 01:24:20.623
as a couple,

01:24:20.723 --> 01:24:22.425
as a family.

01:24:34.470 --> 01:24:36.139
- Well, I made it.

01:24:36.239 --> 01:24:37.406
- [Carol] You must
have been overhead.

01:24:37.506 --> 01:24:38.674
- Good, good, good
to see you again.

01:24:38.774 --> 01:24:39.875
You good?

01:24:39.975 --> 01:24:41.043
If you go like that, you
got one missing lens.

01:24:41.144 --> 01:24:43.379
We were very idealistic.

01:24:43.479 --> 01:24:45.848
We were young kids and

01:24:45.948 --> 01:24:48.484
it seemed like a
beautiful utopia dream.

01:24:48.584 --> 01:24:50.052
We were trying to make it real.

01:24:50.153 --> 01:24:52.255
- [Voiceover] One, two three.

01:24:52.355 --> 01:24:53.856
And again.

01:24:53.956 --> 01:24:55.224
- The Brotherhood
will never end.

01:24:55.324 --> 01:24:57.160
It's in the people that
had that experience,

01:24:57.260 --> 01:24:59.728
that were there, that
experienced that special time.

01:24:59.828 --> 01:25:01.597
It'll be with 'em forever.

